- Buy a Domain 
- Use Route 53  to point to the Ec2  public IP 
d
Step 6: Host Images ,CSS ,JS 
_______
Upload file to : 

/usr/share/nginx/html/
Example : 
sudo nano /usr/share/nginx/html/style.css


